Name: I Am a Rock
About the game: Experience flying in the endless space of the universe and flying over the major planets. Perhaps you will have different ideas about life. Game features : 1. Play as an asteroid or comet, experience flying in the solar system. 2. Plan a flight path to meet up close without touching other planets. 3. Demonstration of the formation of the solar system. 4. Lagrangian Point demonstration. 5. Three-body system demonstration.
